      '❤️ Priority fixes & fastest help',
      '',
      '🧼 ADL checklists + caregiver handoff',
      '❤️ Vital signs tracker (BP, heart, temp, O₂, weight)',
      '🍎 Diabetes logs (sugar numbers, insulin, food)',
      '💊 Medicine helper & MAR (pill times, refills, export)',
      '📝 Daily care logs (notes + photos, reports)',
    ],
